data.title: Casey Desmond
data.meta_description:
Casey Desmond.
Boston, Massachusetts.
Since having appeared on the first season of NBC’s The Voice, award winning songwriter and vocalist Casey Desmond has been writing with hit songwriter Robert Ellis Orrall, & releasing her newest album Déjà Vu on Nov 26th.
